<br>
What pros does the electoral college have?<br>
<br>
What cons does it have?<br>
<br>
What are some compromises to make it a more effective system?<br>
<br>
Pro: Smaller states get attention<br>
<br>
Con: Everyone who voted for the minority in that state loses their votes, the people don't have power - it's the states that have it<br>
<br>
Compromise: Split up the electoral votes based on how many votes each candidate gets<br>
<br>
-Mills <p>&quot;They that can give up essential liberty to obtain a little temporary safety deserve neither liberty nor safety&quot;<br>
